      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning, showroom-quality vehicle! This car is in absolute mint condition, appearing and performing just as it did when it was first manufactured. It has been meticulously maintained and cared for, making it a rare find for any discerning driver looking for perfection.",
