    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential electronic quirks. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance needs.",
